ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_1: The warnings came to the people of Pharaoh.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_2: Warnings also came to the Pharaonites,
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_3: The Pharaoh and his people had also received Our warning,
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_4: And indeed the Noble Messengers came to the people of Firaun.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_5: And indeed, warnings came to the people of Fir`awn.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_6: And certainly the warning came to Firon's people.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_7: The warnings came also to Pharaoh's folk.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_8: And warnings came in truth unto the house of Pharaoh
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_9: Surely warners came to the people of Pharaoh.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_10: And assuredly Unto the household of Fir'awn came the warning.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_11: Certainly the warnings did come to Pharaoh’s clan
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_12: To the People of Pharaoh, too, aforetime, came Warners (from Allah).
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_13: And indeed, warnings came to the people of Fir'aun (Pharaoh) [through Musa (Moses) and Harun (Aaron)].
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_14: The warnings also came to Pharaoh's people,
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_15: The warnings also came to the people of Pharaoh.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_16: And there certainly came to the people of Pharaoh warning.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_17: [54:41] And verily there came to Pharaoh’s folk, his people, together with him, the warnings, the warning by the tongue of Moses and Aaron, but they did not believe.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_18: (And warnings came in truth unto the house of Pharaoh) Moses and Aaron went to Pharaoh and his folk
